{"tid":1026245,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大灣區機遇] 我如何走上愛國路 (1967/68)","createTime":"2019-02-18T03:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T03:26:51.000Z","uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07987fbe4c482470a7ad5393cf66c94ffd72a4ab","tid":1026245,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://forum.hkej.com/node/82373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F82373&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgBF66oQwccw1TbdUPfwT%2FAY%3D&h=1a4c8eea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkej.com/node/82373</a><br />\n<br />\n中四時，正值內地文革（文化大革命）開始。當時，每天上學都會經過海傍，才走到般含道的學校。1967至68年間，我在海傍親眼見到一具具浮屍由珠江漂流至香港；浮屍全是遭人「五花大綁」&mdash;&mdash;反手向後，兩腳往後上屈，手連腳一起綁着，遭人推進河裏&hellip;&hellip;，完全沒有生機。當你看到這種綁得結實的浮屍，心裏很是震撼，很刻骨銘心。"}]}